Package: ecocomDP
Type: Package
Title: Work with datasets in the Ecological Community Design Pattern
Description: Tools to create, use, and convert 'ecocomDP' datasets. 'ecocomDP' is a dataset design pattern for harmonizing ecological community surveys in a research question agnostic format, from source datasets published across multiple repositories, and with methods that keep the derived datasets up-to-date as the underlying sources change.
Version: 1.0.0
